overview: Toronto real estate agent Elli Davis focuses mainly on Toronto condos and is really probably the most experienced real estate agent in Toronto. Elli is “part psychologist, part financial wizard, part negotiator and mediator extraordinaire; she has no equal”. Elli Davis offers Central Toronto real estate for sale, including fine homes and luxury condos in prestigious neighbourhoods such as Forest Hill, Rosedale, the Yonge Street Corridor, Waterfront, Moore Park, Lawrence Park, Deer Park, Chaplin Estates, Allenby and the Avenue Road/Lawrence area. Elli concentrates on selling homes and condominiums in the north and central neighbourhoods of Metro Toronto. She has a wealth of knowledge when it comes to urban living and is a master negotiator. She also offers a referral service tapping into a network of other top agents worldwide. If you or someone you know is considering buying or selling a home out of town, Elli will gladly refer you to an Agent who specializes in your particular area.
